---
title: Logistikos — Order lifecycle state machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> processing: Customer submits order
    processing --> open: Geocoding + routing + matching OK
    processing --> error: Geocoding or routing fails
    error --> processing: Customer corrects address
    open --> accepted: Driver accepts (optimistic lock)
    open --> expired: Stale order cleanup (cron)
    open --> cancelled: Customer cancels
    accepted --> pickup_in_progress: Driver starts pickup
    accepted --> cancelled: Either party cancels
    pickup_in_progress --> in_transit: Goods collected
    in_transit --> completed: Delivery confirmed
    completed --> [*]
    cancelled --> [*]
    expired --> [*]

    note right of processing
        Background tasks:
        GeocodeWorker → RouteWorker
        → PriceEstimationWorker
        → DriverMatchWorker
    end note

    note right of accepted
        Side effects:
        PaymentAuthorizationWorker
        FeedInvalidation
        RouteSnapshot cache
        CustomerNotification
    end note

    note right of completed
        Side effects:
        PaymentCaptureWorker
        DriverEarning created
        GPS tracking stopped
    end note

    note right of cancelled
        Side effects:
        PaymentRefundWorker
        FeedInvalidation
        CounterpartNotification
    end note
